
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>The purpose of this eMail is twofold.</p>
    <ul>
      <li> Distribute a letter from the Commander of VFW Post 8600 to all members that includes important information on our current status and plans</li>
      <li> Request that you validate your basic contact and status information and provide any changed or missing information</li>

    </ul>
    <p>
      Current Member Information<br>
      --------------------------
    </p>
    <div>Status: <%= @member.status %></div>
    <div>Pay Status: <%= @member.pay_status %></div>

    <% days_remaining = nil %>
    <% if @member.status != 'Life' && @member.paid_thru.present? %>
      <% days_remaining = (Chronic.parse(@member.paid_thru).to_date - Date.today).to_i %>
      <div>Pay Thru: <%= @member.paid_thru %></div>
      <div>Days Remaining: <%= days_remaining %></div>

    <% end %>
    <div>Name: <%= @member.name %></div>
    <div>Address: <%= @member.address %></div>
    <div>City: <%= @member.city %>, State: <%= @member.state %>, Zip: <%= @member.zip %> </div>
    <div>Phone: <%= @member.phone.present? ? @member.phone : "Missing" %></div>
    <div>Email: <%= @member.email.present? ? @member.email : "Missing" %></div>

    <p>
      <p>You can reply to this eMail or send new eMail to the post at <b>vfwpost8600@gmail.com</b> and identify changes or corrections.</p>
      <p>You can call the post at <b>256-546-2440</b> and identify changes/corrections or leave a voice mail. We have very limited open hours but we've added a 'Voice Attendant'. You can press '2' during the voice attendant message and leave a voice mail. </p>
    </p>
    <% if days_remaining.present? && days_remaining < 0 %>
      <p>  Your VFW membership has expired. Please contact the Post and we may be able to help you with your membership dues.</p>
    <% end %>
    <br>
    <p>
      Commander's Letter<br>
      ----------------------------
    </p>

  </body>
</html>